FEICA is composed of 15 European National Associations, 21 Direct Company Members and 17 Affiliate Company Members. &#xd;
&#xd;
We represent at the European level about 750 producers of adhesives and sealants of which the vast majority are SMEs.&#xd;
&#xd;
The total European market for A&amp;S is projected to grow annually 2.5 to 3.0% in terms of volume and 3.5 to 4.0% in terms of value in 2016 and 2017. Growth will differ significantly from country to country.
